                <head>No. 81.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Morton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-12-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 28, 1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The withdrawal of the decrees of 27th November, which will be published
                    to-morrow, limits the time for the admission of American pork products to the
                    20th January at the ports of Havre, Bordeaux, and Marseilles instead of
                    Nantes.</p>
                <p>Telegram of yesterday received this morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>MORTON.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
